It`s not! an ISO image this numb nut has just ISO`d the video TS folder, you`ll just waste your disc`s if you try to burn this as an image.
Mount it first in a virtual drive and then import the video ts folder into your burning software for burning.Proves the point that even if you don`t know what your doing you can still get a skull !.
